{"id":239160,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/07/维权网-陕西咸阳村民送材料在法院遭袭击（图）/","date":"2012-07-11T02:31:10Z","modified":"2012-07-11T02:31:10Z","title":"维权网 | 陕西咸阳村民送材料在法院遭袭击（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员张成报道）此前本网曾经多次关注报道，北京律师吕国华为陕西咸阳市秦都区陈杨寨街道村民杨志海、石海梅等人代理拆迁案子，遭遇当地政府工作人员围殴。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>上午，陕西省高级法院针对此案作出行政裁定，责令咸阳市秦都区法院立案受理</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>位尚未搬迁的当事人诉秦都区国土分局案件。按照法律规定，诉讼期间不得启动非诉执行程序。陕西高法对两户已经执行拆迁的当事人仍拒绝立案。然而，同日下午秦都区法院发公告，责令当事人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13</span><span>日前搬迁，逾期则强制执行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>上午，村民按陕西高法要求去咸阳秦都法院送材料，在法院遭多名暴徒袭击后强行带走，诉讼文书也被撕毁。受害村民不清楚施暴者的身份。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>日</span><span>吕国华律师表示，虽然收到扬言灭口的电话，自己依然要去咸阳参加开庭。自己托咸阳群众买了墓碑，决心已定。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>另外，强拆暴徒还通过拆除相邻建筑的方法把尚未搬迁的居民房屋弄成危房，完全不顾村民的安危。然而村民们也没有被吓倒，一位被强制执行的村民在废墟上搭建帐篷，继续抗争。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>相关报道请参见：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/06/blog-post_4531.html\">http://wqw2010.blogspot.com/2012/06/blog-post_4531.html</a></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-RlWE363zwl0/T_zi6rHNI8I/AAAAAAAAJJw/CfAVPuKDV-U/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"161\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-RlWE363zwl0/T_zi6rHNI8I/AAAAAAAAJJw/CfAVPuKDV-U/s320/2.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Y0da1zWQ9pA/T_zi-vkKYmI/AAAAAAAAJJ4/2d4CBGjJnhk/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"220\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Y0da1zWQ9pA/T_zi-vkKYmI/AAAAAAAAJJ4/2d4CBGjJnhk/s320/3.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-1148649766657178101?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2012/07/ff7decb12.jpg-150x150.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}